replyContent: There's more than one dictionary option for English. One of them accepts the word QI. You can choose the best for you. Oh, and all words played by the AI are valid.

content: US slang and short form accepted but few proper English-language words and words like sheriff must be spelled with one f. Really disappointing for a scrabble player and English speaker.
replyContent:
I'm sorry you are disappointed with this app. As a matter of fact we're working to improve exactly this right now. The app is based on the SOWPODS word list, which is the biggest one. We're thinking of letting the user choose from different word lists and improve the AI so that the droid won't play very rare words.
ps: sheriff is correct
